{"tid":1013062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【痴撚線】柏景灣巴士站五米高電錶房頂傳惡臭　報警揭有腐屍","createTime":"2019-02-08T05:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T07:40:24.000Z","uid":23707,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"34cbdd092b6f58691610a5ac74dca031cc9b5ced","tid":1013062,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"今早九時許，警方接報稱，大角咀海庭道18號柏景灣巴士總站一個電錶房頂發現一具屍體，警員隨即報往現場調查。該具屍體早已發脹發臭，估計已死者已死去十多日。據知，該電錶房鄰近九巴茶水間，數日前已有小巴司機於上址聞到強烈臭味，遂報警求助，惟當時未尋獲臭味源頭。今早有機電署人員爬上電錶房頂檢查時，卻發現一具屍體。警員在屍體身上發現有他人的財物，現正留守調查死因及死者身份，機電署人員亦在場了解。現場彌漫強烈屍臭，死者身穿牛仔褲。"},{"pid":"0d93efaff95b8cbd605ba50cbf1fd875e22eb5f1","tid":1013062,"uid":3668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e3f699be2944d238d791106a117faf71130004","tid":1013062,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊隻巴膠黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"d170c50f6724e2504a2da057a24681e5df6d7eab","tid":1013062,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"香港真係死"},{"pid":"5091bc600de1b8282c05c5ba7e9ac2c7b16f7b1b","tid":1013062,"uid":96068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"Cls 香港搞乜"},{"pid":"f3c6baf5df3d6428ec182590786c98e2153c3bb4","tid":1013062,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"10 幾日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起都臭<br />\n前幾日過年仲要咁熱又曬住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b1d3bc3159bcf848c3f3a8fd3bb0a08f944f73","tid":1013062,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-